Thartryn Ilistar III was the eleventh King of the Ilistar Dynasty who ruled the city-state of Westgate. He was also the last Ilistar King of Westgate.
Thartryn III began his rule when his father, King Halcoranth, died in the . He only reigned for a few years before succumbing to plague, along with the remainder of the Ilistar heirs, in the .
